96b9c486-fcc2-4efc-93a7-03b71a6504a5.title: Chief servant
96b9c486-fcc2-4efc-93a7-03b71a6504a5.text: Welcome to the Ardougne Domestic Service Agency!

options.text: I'd like to dismiss my servant, please.

146ad3f6-caea-41d7-997a-1f3473d7ed71.title: <player>
146ad3f6-caea-41d7-997a-1f3473d7ed71.text: I'd like to dismiss my servant, please.

options.text: Yes, I want to dismiss my servant.
No, I'll keep my servant for now.

28ade7d3-30cb-4fcf-a816-f30fcb1d16eb.title: <player>
28ade7d3-30cb-4fcf-a816-f30fcb1d16eb.text: No, I'll keep my servant for now.

2ef762df-849c-4b1e-8f87-c62821aab517.title: <player>
2ef762df-849c-4b1e-8f87-c62821aab517.text: Yes, I want to dismiss my servant.

dd7e8115-ba4c-46e0-a99f-b33c3a619ff7.title: Chief servant
dd7e8115-ba4c-46e0-a99f-b33c3a619ff7.text: Very well, you no longer have a servant.

417bc7a7-a800-46fc-8a16-967b1ca7f81d.title: Chief servant
417bc7a7-a800-46fc-8a16-967b1ca7f81d.text:
According to our records, one of our people is already
working for you. If you want to hire a different one
you will have to dismiss them.

3ea50147-6f65-4c6f-affb-456e473c3844.title: Chief servant
3ea50147-6f65-4c6f-affb-456e473c3844.text:
Certainly! We have a number of servants here now
looking for work. Why not have a chat to them and see
which one you would like to hire?

f919ffe6-32cc-43df-8f83-a14973a2d37c.title: Chief servant
f919ffe6-32cc-43df-8f83-a14973a2d37c.text:
Do you need help around your house? Our trained,
efficient workers are ready to serve you.

ac926841-2a4a-485d-85db-c0b1e31a75a9.title: Chief servant
ac926841-2a4a-485d-85db-c0b1e31a75a9.text:
They can cook meals for you and your friends, make
tea, serve drinks, greet guests, and even take items to
and from the bank for you.

34dcae6a-7193-4bd4-890e-aa943abf67bd.title: Chief servant
34dcae6a-7193-4bd4-890e-aa943abf67bd.text:
The more expensive servants will be able to make trips
to the bank more quickly. Some of them can also go to
the sawmill to change logs to planks for you.

74b25748-0611-4ca7-be27-f3c9bed5bad4.title: Chief servant
74b25748-0611-4ca7-be27-f3c9bed5bad4.text:
Remember, you'll need to keep paying your servant.
You pay them once when you hire them, and then
they'll periodically ask for wages. You can dismiss your
servant at any time.
